      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPARKIE DEVINE (2) is a four-year-old mare from the Ashley Ainsworth stable on debut. No excuses from this advantageous draw. Has strong trial form coming into this. Makes plenty of appeal. ARIVADERCHI (5) is in good form with top-five finishes at his last four starts, most recently recording a second over 2150m at Bendigo. Meets a similar line up so he can play a significant role. DELIGHTFUL REYNA (6) is a two-year-old filly from the Alison Alford stable on debut. Trial winner who looks above average. Will be right there at the business end. MAORIS AVENGER (3) missed the placings two runs back then did a great job to finish 30 metres back in third despite breaking in the run over 2200m at Horsham a week ago. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. Only needs to get things right to be in the money again.",
